entries.title: Newport Beach Film Fest: Ewan McGregor Set for TV Performance of the Year Honor and Live ‘Awards Chatter’ Podcast
entries.summary: Ewan McGregor, the veteran Scottish actor who recently earned some of the best reviews of his 30-year career for his performance at the center of the Paramount+ limited series A Gentleman in Moscow, on which he also served as an executive producer, has been tapped for the Newport Beach Film Festival’s TV Performance of the […]
